Arrow Â– The TV series Arrow is a great program for fans of green arrow and lovers of the DC universe. The series tells a story about a young man named Oliver Queen, his farther, a sea captain and a young girl out on the ocean taking a cruise on their expensive boat when a storm strikes and kills the young girl. The rest of them escape unharmed drifting along the water hoping to find land. After many hours food starts to run out and there is only a small amount of water for one person. Oliver's farther decides to kill himself in order to save Oliver. As many days alone on the water Oliver find an island where he meets a Chinese hunter. On the island many things happen including becoming the Protector of central city, the arrow.